import re

def extract_html_attributes(html_string):
    pattern = ''
    matches = re.findall(pattern, html_string)
    attributes = []
    for match in matches:
        attr_pattern = '(\\w+)=["\\\']([^"\\\']*)["\\\']'
        attrs = re.findall(attr_pattern, match)
        for attr in attrs:
            attributes.append(f'{attr[0]}="{attr[1]}"')
    return attributes
